OL,3,CBurnham announces #2 bus fare cap from
OL,4,CJanuary
OL,6,FSingle bus fares across England will
OL,7,Fbe capped at #2 from January, Prime
OL,8,FMinister Andy Burnham has announced.
OL,10,FThe nationwide cap is currently set at
OL,11,F#3 until the end of March 2027
OL,12,Falthough some areas ` including London
OL,13,Fand Greater Manchester, where Mr
OL,14,FBurnham set a #2 limit as mayor ` have
OL,15,Flower top rates for single tickets.
OL,17,FMr Burnham said: "Good, affordable
OL,18,Ftransport links are an essential. No
OL,19,Fone should be priced out of those and
OL,20,Fleft behind.
OL,26,@yD@ROU
