OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784719105
OL,3,CBurnham announces #2 bus fare cap from
OL,4,CJanuary
OL,6,F"But for too long people have said
OL,7,Fthat cheaper transport isn't an
OL,8,Foption. I don't accept that. I've done
OL,9,Fit before and I will do it again now:
OL,10,Fa #2 cap on bus fares for millions
OL,11,Facross the country.
OL,13,F"Lower fares will help people get to
OL,14,Fwhere they need to ` giving them
OL,15,Fbreathing space to help with the cost
OL,16,Fof living."
OL,18,FThe measure is backed by #454 million
OL,19,Fof funding ` including money to allow
OL,20,Fdevolved governments to take similar
OL,21,Faction.
