OL,3,CBurnham announces #2 bus fare cap from
OL,4,CJanuary
OL,6,FSome #400 million of that funding will
OL,7,Fcome from switching investment in
OL,8,Finternational climate finance to
OL,9,Floans, with the rest from savings in
OL,10,Fthe Department for Energy Security and
OL,11,FNet Zero budget.
OL,13,FThe total cost of the scheme is
OL,14,Fexpected to be more than #500 million,
OL,15,Fwith the rest coming from Department
OL,16,Ffor Transport funding already
OL,17,Fallocated to buses.
