OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784719105
OL,3,CBurnham announces #2 bus fare cap from
OL,4,CJanuary
OL,6,FThe #2 cap will be in place throughout
OL,7,F2027 and reverses an increase put in
OL,8,Fplace by Sir Keir Starmer and Rachel
OL,9,FReeves in 2024.
OL,11,FA #2 cap had been in place between
OL,12,FJanuary 2023 and December 2024 but the
OL,13,Fincoming Labour administration argued
OL,14,Fit was not affordable, although some
OL,15,Fmetro mayors, including Mr Burnham,
OL,16,Fdecided to fund an extension of the
OL,17,Flower limit in their areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
