OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784719105
OL,3,CBurnham announces #2 bus fare cap from
OL,4,CJanuary
OL,6,FChancellor John Healey said "millions
OL,7,Fof people" would benefit from fares
OL,8,Fbeing slashed by a third and insisted
OL,9,Fthe measure could be paid for.
OL,11,F"This action to ease the cost of
OL,12,Fliving is funded by savings made
OL,13,Felsewhere, so there's no burden to
OL,14,FBritish taxpayers, just pounds going
OL,15,Fback into their pockets," he said.
OL,17,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,18,Fsaid the move would make "everyday
OL,19,Fjourneys easier and cheaper".
